Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回家!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那個孩子  羽鳥智世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在日本已經被認定為死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在這裡隨便找個地區登記了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩你了  阿道夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不  反而要謝謝你告訴我她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,「夜之愛子」可是很珍貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有資質和意願的孩子是寶貴的財產吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是喜歡喝酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜歡和你一起喝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這是愛麗絲送的聖誕節禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只許喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你們閒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,托利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼你們兩個臉色都這麼差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,進來的時候請安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我也來陪你們喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,別隨便亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手臂還沒痊癒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙是叫卡達飛爾斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後你還有跟他接觸過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真好  也介紹給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他是跨世紀的漂流魔術師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,長生不老可是永恆的主題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是無聊的痴夢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是有潔癖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然你很優秀  但是這樣會樹敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴有幾個人就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,來  來  來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,托利  不能再多喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼  再來一點也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是優秀的話  就不會被那種傢伙威脅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼情況  超有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那種狀態還會持續4小時  所以接下來就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼情況  超麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:05.31,Comment,,0,0,0,,你也來喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,阿道夫  救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,別拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼情況  除了阿道夫還有別人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,梅里托利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,牠是我老師的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,倫敦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不知為何  覺得身體沒什麼重量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想咳嗽也咳不出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,感受不到冷暖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,請問你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,卡達飛爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是叫卡達飛爾斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐全身都透明  難道是幽靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這可不行  要去你該去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因為不這樣就很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,卡達…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不叫那個被詛咒的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,卡達飛爾斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫…約瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,卡達飛爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎麼做我們才能獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你去誰那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙…卡達飛爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一直環繞在耳畔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是第幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是睡了兩天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼林德爾家的塞爾克在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你總算醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲  為什麼你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我去告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,出了點麻煩  或者說有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服隨便穿一件就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,話說愛麗絲你多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,今年18歲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,早安  智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,託你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亞斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,託你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,能觀察到活著的「夜之愛子」這還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,能見到你真是很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你能活著真是太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,雖不想承認  但他是我的同輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我代替他向你表示歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是阿道夫·史特勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,之前真是對不住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是托利·伊尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,請叫我托利就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是學院的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,學院?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒聽他說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,閒話就到這裡  趕緊進入正題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,最近在龍之國有幼龍遭到了偷獵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有兩頭被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,偷獵者在現場留下了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我做的移動裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的事情大概是卡達飛爾斯幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,手臂被奪走的時候似乎連製作方法也一併偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這沒什麼  我很清楚這並不是你的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,問題在於為什麼我們要一起去找卡達飛爾斯和幼龍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你們跟龍之國的關係很好  而且也親眼見過卡達飛爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再說了為什麼學院要去尋找幼龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,林德爾大人跟學院之間簽有著協定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,跟林德爾?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是為了被束縛在那裡的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能否幫我們找到幼龍  送回他的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一是跟我們無關  二是十分危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你該不會忘記自己的身體有多脆弱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亞斯才是  該不會是忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你十分疼痛  非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,正如艾利亞斯說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有義務就沒有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那些幼龍跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,並不是出於自己的意願離開龍之國的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,知道曾與我一同玩過的那些孩子遭受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想袖手旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我答應合作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微變了點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼你們有什麼線索或是頭緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,卡達飛爾斯那邊毫無頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,幼龍那邊就交給林德爾繼續追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可能兩頭龍都意識模糊  現在得不到什麼有用的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得卡達飛爾斯應該在倫敦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然只是我的直覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,史特勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,龍很值錢嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,當然  還相當貴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,或許會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  誰能把電話借我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是您啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,最近怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,對  我現在人在巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是工作的話  會根據報酬和內容來判斷是否受理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊給我更加用力按住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,賽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見  智世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這位是恩滋華斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法和魔術這些按規定是禁止在拍賣場使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這我有聽說  所以我並沒有使用魔法和魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只是把身體從頭到尾徹底重組了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,既不是賽門也不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這形象到底是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,關於大家的名字我就不過問了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想把這個拿去拍賣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我會把它排在下午拍賣會的第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這之後才開始正式的拍賣  這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,龍的拍賣將於18點開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在這之前請各位隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真是什麼都有賣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,智世  請收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,支票和牌板嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對於您的賣出價  我們將其一半的錢匯進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一半的錢嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,作為這裡曾經的商品以及如今的賣方這是你應得的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,龍十分昂貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,學院的經費要是不夠的話  請拿去使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,錢嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來這本來就是艾利亞斯的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你的氣氛完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,個頭也長高了  跟那時相比簡直判若兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有改變的地方  也有沒變的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人的核心部分是不會那麼容易改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,撇開好壞不談  你是個十分頑固的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼  你們在聊些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你要來我們這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在家的話  家裡會有人寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,立場堅定這是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼想說的就說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒把學院的事告訴她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子是不會去學院的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以沒有跟她說的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,信使鳥怎麼了  是壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,連富烈德這可不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然這麼執泥於「夜之愛子」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不是在意「夜之愛子」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只是擔心作為人類的她的將來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就算現在沒事  只要她的依存對象還只是你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那她今後還能成長多少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有資格說這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,讓走投無路的人背負起知識的金庫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,再強行讓其登上開往未來的船隻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,假裝一副為其指明路的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,讓對方覺得別無他選
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們其實也沒什麼區別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會你其實並不想成為魔術師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是被人強迫…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,別擅自決定我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她也是這樣期待著的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就看看你們能持續到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,生物是會改變的  無論是否是自己所期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不過那把骨頭完全都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是給別人鋪好鐵軌讓其前行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,結果選擇走自己的道路的人比比皆是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是走在自己選擇的道路上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我想走哪裡  那裡就是我的路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,年輕真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼18點的拍賣現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這是來自如今已經鎖閉的北方龍之國
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡土生土長的純翼龍的幼龍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼從80萬開始叫價
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,81
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,82
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,85
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,90  90!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,92
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,100
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,學院的極限是150
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要是超過的話  那時候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,委託人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,122
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是僱傭的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.01,Comment,,0,0,0,,125
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是僱傭的人所僱傭過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,125  125
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人在看著我們這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,150  有人開價150了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要追價到多少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,到你所知道的餘額上限為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,160
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,170!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,還有客人繼續出價嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小妹妹  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧  除了你以外誰也聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可以說是正巧給你利用的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,正巧利用…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,180
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,180
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,185
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,185
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,191
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,191
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,193
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,193
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,197
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我們的資金見底了就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不行的話  就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我們思念傳達的約定  真讓人遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,請各位客人千萬別讓自己後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,還有人出價嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,260
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,290
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,290
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒有問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,290…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,290了  還有更高的價格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是專用的強化咒縛式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼還能扯開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道  這是頭一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,已經發狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,智世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,牠想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,牠很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,還非常厭惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你能聽到龍的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的  那不是你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不需要跟隨這股感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,龍的悲哀咆哮  在倫敦的天空迴響著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,為了拯救龍  少女所得出的結論…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是那麼的殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的  一起回去吧
